title: Did Megan Rapinoe Say ‘Gross Men Like Trump’ Are the Reason Women ‘Go Gay’?
subtitle: U.S. soccer star Rapinoe is definitely an outspoken critic of President Donald Trump.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: U.S. women's soccer forward Megan Rapinoe said "gross men" like U.S. President Donald Trump make women "go gay."
